          <title>Red Rocks clinch Big 12 regular season title</title>
          <description><![CDATA[SALT LAKE CITY (ABC4 Sports) - The University of Utah claimed the Big 12 Conference’s first gymnastics regular-season title. The Red Rocks earned the title Friday after a 198.075-197.525 victory against Denver to go 6-0 during league play.]]></description>
