          <title>New York Yankees drop ban on beards, 49 years after it was imposed by owner George Steinbrenner</title>
          <description><![CDATA[TAMPA. Fla. (AP) — The New York Yankees dropped their ban on beards Friday, 49 years after it was imposed by owner George Steinbrenner, in a move aimed to improve player recruitment as the team tries to win its first World Series title since 2009.]]></description>
